title: 安装traincarts插件服务器报错

replies.author: 思念化作海
replies.txt_content:
Since April 16, 2017 release version names will be in a MCVersion-pluginversion format. Older versions of Minecraft are also supported.
虽然说是兼容旧版本的 但建议换v1.12.2版本的插件 或者是此插件再CatServer上不兼容
试试在paperspigot端上运行看看能不能使用
